race.comment: HARA'S PEST (7) boasts a strong record this journey with seven wins and 10 minors from 21 tries. Recorded a 3.5 lengths win (21.72) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. PROFESSOR SAMSON (8) is a last start winner who can measure up again. FLYING SEAL (3) solid performance after tracking the speed to score in a Grade 5 by 0.5 len at this track over 390m (22.12). Racing well and can win again.
